'''马里奥·德拉吉'''（{{lang-it|Mario Draghi}}，{{IPA-it|ˈmaːrjo ˈdraːɡi}}；{{bd|1947年|9月3日||}}），[[意大利|意大利]]银行家，经济学家，现任[[意大利部長會議主席|義大利總理]]。曾任[[欧洲中央银行行长|欧洲中央银行行长]]及[[意大利银行|意大利银行]]行长。他还是[[欧洲中央银行|欧洲中央银行]]理事会成员，和[[国际清算银行|国际清算银行]][[董事会|董事会]]成员。2021年2月3日，義大利總統[[塞爾焦·馬達雷拉|塞爾焦·馬達雷拉]]授權德拉吉組建新政府<ref>{{Cite web|title=意大利總統授權經濟學家德拉吉組建新政府-香港商報|url=http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-02/04/content_1247243.html|accessdate=2021-02-06|work=www.hkcd.com|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204083459/http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-02/04/content_1247243.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歐洲央行行長==
2011年6月24日经[[歐洲議會|歐洲議會]]批准将从2011年11月接替[[让-克洛德·特里谢|让-克洛德·特里谢]]任[[欧洲中央银行|欧洲中央银行]]行長。德拉吉靠大量寬鬆政策來拯救陷入[[歐洲主權債務危機|歐洲主權債務危機]]的歐元區國家，解決了歐元危機。自此債市成功被安撫下來。

==意大利總理==
2021年1月孔特总理辞职後，德拉吉獲邀籌組新內閣。外界期望他能以拯救歐元區的經驗，讓這危機重重的國家復甦。最終他組成嚢括了大多數政黨，再加上他在內的獨立人士和專家的[[大聯合政府|大聯合政府]]。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-02-11|title=Dal voto Cinquestelle via libera al governo Draghi con il 59,3%. Di Maio: “Il movimento prende la via europea”. Fico: “Niente salti ne buio”|url=https://www.lastampa.it/politica/2021/02/11/news/al-via-il-voto-su-rousseau-fico-voto-si-il-momento-del-paese-e-molto-delicato-1.39887941|access-date=2021-02-11|website=lastampa.it|language=it|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213131123/https://www.lastampa.it/politica/2021/02/11/news/al-via-il-voto-su-rousseau-fico-voto-si-il-momento-del-paese-e-molto-delicato-1.39887941|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==家庭 ==
1973年，马里奥·德拉吉与英国文学专家塞雷娜·卡佩罗结婚，两人育有两子<ref name=rep140619>[https://roma.repubblica.it/cronaca/2021/02/03/news/chi_e_serena_cappello_la_moglie_di_mario_draghi_lei_ne_sa_piu_di_me_-285764078/ Chi è Serena Cappello la moglie di Mario Draghi: "Lei ne sa più di me"] {{Wayback|url=https://roma.repubblica.it/cronaca/2021/02/03/news/chi_e_serena_cappello_la_moglie_di_mario_draghi_lei_ne_sa_piu_di_me_-285764078/ |date=20211220140053 }}, ''la Repubblica''</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Who is Serena Cappello, Draghi's wife. He said: "She knows more" {{!}} Italy24 News English|url=https://www.italy24news.com/en/2021/02/who-is-serena-cappello-draghis-wife-he-said-she-knows-more.html|access-date=2021-02-16|language=en-US|archive-date=21 February 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221060511/https://www.italy24news.com/en/2021/02/who-is-serena-cappello-draghis-wife-he-said-she-knows-more.html|url-status=dead}}</ref>。费德利卡·德拉吉曾担任基内斯特拉温泉的投资总监和意大利生物技术天使会的董事会成员；吉亚科莫·德拉吉为金融分析师，曾在投资银行摩根士丹利担任利率衍生品交易员，现供职于LMR Partners对冲基金。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-08/giacomo-draghi-said-to-exit-morgan-stanley-for-hedge-fund-lmr|title=Giacomo Draghi Said to Exit Morgan Stanley for Hedge Fund|date=14 June 2019|access-date=14 June 2019|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022192404/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-08/giacomo-draghi-said-to-exit-morgan-stanley-for-hedge-fund-lmr|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.repubblica.it/economia/finanza/2017/02/08/news/il_figlio_di_mario_draghi_lascia_morgan_stanley_per_un_fondo_hedge-157861230/|title=Il figlio di Mario Draghi lascia Morgan Stanley per un fondo hedge|date=8 February 2017|website=Repubblica.it|language=it|access-date=14 June 2019|archive-date=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220141606/https://www.repubblica.it/economia/finanza/2017/02/08/news/il_figlio_di_mario_draghi_lascia_morgan_stanley_per_un_fondo_hedg